{"tid":643501,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)逃出絕命鎮 午夜人肉列車 絕世天劫","createTime":"2018-04-26T14:14:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-26T19:08:18.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"25c53c1df4bf953964eb0ce9af6f0acfecbebde4","tid":643501,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T14:14:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=7rqFycSoXiR%2BlvFX%2B%2FLSDARJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=a4d37c1d\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=7rqFycSoXiR%2BlvFX%2B%2FLSDARJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=32ec3184\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有OKRU睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=7rqFycSoXiR%2BlvFX%2B%2FLSDARJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=5fd72a19\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/6/60/Get_Out_Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F6%2F60%2FGet_Out_Poster.jpg&h=364dd882&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://i3.photobucket.com/albums/y83/raura1020/midnightmeattrainposter.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi3.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Fy83%2Fraura1020%2Fmidnightmeattrainposter.jpg&h=e1eb8b62&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/f/fc/Armageddon-poster06.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Ff%2Ffc%2FArmageddon-poster06.jpg&h=891e86ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.故事敘述一名非裔男性克里斯（丹尼爾&middot;卡盧亞 飾）與一名白人女孩露絲（愛莉森&middot;威廉絲 飾）相互愛侶，兩人準備到女方父母家中拜訪時，克里斯開始漸漸地察覺自己與女方的父母關係有些不對勁，誰也沒想到某個種族陰謀竟在背後偷偷醞釀著...<br />\n<br />\n2.劇情是說里昂［Leon Kauffman］是一名藝術系夜校生，白天以攝影師為業，到處拍攝各式各樣的照片糊口，在友人的建議下，里昂開始在夜車裡半偷窺似的拍攝晚歸的夜車人群，在每個月台與車廂之間穿梭，卻也意外目睹一宗殘忍的兇殺案。深受刺激的他，企圖追縱連續殺人魔地鐵屠夫的下落，卻發現事實沒有想像中簡單，跑去報警卻被警察認為是偷拍狂，而且也讓殺人魔將目標轉向了自己&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n3.地球即將被跟德州一樣大的隕石撞擊，為了毀滅隕石，美國國家航空暨太空總署決定派人在隕石上挖一個洞直到核心，放一顆炸彈在裡面引爆，從內部炸開隕石。布魯斯威力演的史哈利在中國擁有油田，是公認成功的石油大老闆。他並不信任他一個年輕屬下小傑，因此也不爽他女兒蕾跟他交往..<br />\n<br />\n10 30PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=7rqFycSoXiR%2BlvFX%2B%2FLSDARJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=41023111\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=7rqFycSoXiR%2BlvFX%2B%2FLSDARJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=f73b4bac\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4587dca4575c976caa55f22676ba576e0c645fa2","tid":643501,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-26